Marisol Padilla Sánchez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marisol_Padilla_S%C3%A1nchez 0 Marisol Padilla Sánchez is an American actress. She is best known for her roles in the films L. A. Confidential and Traffic. The End of Violance Directed by Wim Wenders, Before night falls Directed by Julian Schnabel She lives in Guadalajara, Mexico with her family, working as both an Actress and as an Acting Coach, supporting up-and-coming Actors and Mexican filmmakers and working on personal film projects.
